### 1️⃣ Get all images
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images


### 2️⃣ Get one image (replace <IMAGE_ID> with a real _id from step 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a84f3f0a7262d7e013998e


### 3️⃣ Rename the image (PATCH name)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a84f3f0a7262d7e013998e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Blue merle herding sheep"
}


### 4️⃣ Fetch the same image again to verify update
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a84f3f0a7262d7e013998e